  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> Idle\n    Idle --> Loading: Start Request\n    Loading --> Success: Data Received\n    Loading --> Error: Request Failed\n    Success --> Idle: Reset\n    Error --> Idle: Retry\n    Error --> [*]: Abort\n",
  "diagram_type": "state size:150..250",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T04:04:17.016970",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个数据加载的状态机，从初始状态进入Idle，然后用户触发Start Request后进入Loading。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Start Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那Loading之后应该有两个分支吧？一个是成功拿到数据，另一个是请求失败？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Loading到Success的触发条件是Data Received，到Error则是Request Failed。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Data Received",
        "Request Failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把这两个分支加上去了。那Success和Error之后怎么回到Idle？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Success之后用Reset回到Idle，Error之后用Retry也能回到Idle。不过Error还多一个选择——Abort直接终止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Idle",
        "Reset",
        "Error",
        "Retry",
        "Abort",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，Abort是从Error直接到终止状态对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "[*]",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，你写的是Error到Idle的触发条件是Abort，这不对。Abort应该是结束流程，Retry才是回Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Retry",
        "Abort",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "抱歉搞混了，已经修正：Error -- Idle是Retry，Error -- [*]才是Abort。现在状态流转应该都对了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Retry",
        "[*]",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了，Idle、Loading、Success、Error四个状态，所有流转都符合业务逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
